{"tid":2369624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"酒吧業界憂3月再引發結業潮　冀政府容許復業","createTime":"2021-01-17T10:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T04:28:54.000Z","uid":70964,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"558e5ace932d95ace7ba827f675bf5566839a9cd","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:15:26.000Z","msg":"做唔到咪執囉, <br />\n做生意一定賺? 輸打贏要?<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n自第四波疫情，酒吧業界停業近一個半月，香港酒吧業協會副主席錢雋永說，業界處於水深火熱之中，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">他們願意勸籲市民使用「安心岀行」應用程式，進入酒吧前掃描二維碼，希望政府容許業界復業。</span></span>他說現時已有一成酒吧結業，若不盡快復業，業界難以生存，預計到3月會引發結業潮，有再多一至兩成酒吧結業，約5000名從業員受影響。他又指，部分酒吧仍未能領取第三輪防疫抗疫基金資助，令經營更困難。有業內人士說，酒吧界停業的同時，部分提供酒精飲品的餐廳仍繼續營業，批評政府的防疫措施不公平和有漏洞，要求一視同仁；又認為疫情反覆，業界停業的犧牲是無意義，已是「<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">忍無可忍</span></span>」 。有酒吧職員說，因酒吧停業而失業，已用光儲蓄，嚴重影響生計。"},{"pid":"92c47db5d2973f52c96017f6e42158e7a137eee0","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93ccd824c3aa194ec06fcd97c597db786f4bb8f7","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:17:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea8d89d9cdbca232d41bc48b398515e5a968fb91","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:17:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c775d9dccb4a9f1b662ed0e94d04650a9991651","tid":2369624,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"其實有好多酒吧偷雞開緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n灣仔果堆夜晚多人過年宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a2beb941143a70ee782862a06dd36d223d88a7","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c775d9dccb4a9f1b662ed0e94d04650a9991651","tid":2369624,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"其實有好多酒吧偷雞開緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n灣仔果堆夜晚多人過年宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"有牌o個d 邊敢做呀<br />\n釘牌"},{"pid":"b166ba047c4588745d3692ef7f23138cc3e1be83","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"按錯正評 屌"},{"pid":"a719aa6376f546fb322157cd0639417ccc4b9930","tid":2369624,"uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾成日話執<br />\n執撚三成年都仲未執得哂<br />\n真係打不死的小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804f3aa2e4b0e233b75ca67a43cfb31e5ab4c61e","tid":2369624,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"講左成年都未見大規模結業"},{"pid":"ae8f1b2f52df7daca9fdfa752844f95adac26d4b","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a719aa6376f546fb322157cd0639417ccc4b9930","tid":2369624,"uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾成日話執<br />\n執撚三成年都仲未執得哂<br />\n真係打不死的小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2285789/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2285789/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a8e563f552c34800a1c76a227320c797ae679dc4","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804f3aa2e4b0e233b75ca67a43cfb31e5ab4c61e","tid":2369624,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"講左成年都未見大規模結業"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"政府宣布收緊酒吧每枱人數至不多於2人，及堂食時間至晚上12時前。<br />\n<br />\n香港持牌酒吧會所聯會創會會長梁立仁對措施表示失望及憤慨。他表示，只能營運至12時前，生意額將跌至不足兩成；早前放寬營運時間到凌晨2時後，生意額回升至4成，業界勉強可以疫情中繼續慢慢捱，形容失去黃金兩小時，會令業界難以生存，預計會出現一輪倒閉潮。<br />\n<br />\n調酒師工會主席侯翠珊質疑，收緊多兩小時，對於防疫的效用不大。她表示，有會員已準備放無薪假，又批評專家將幼稚園與酒吧相比的言論毫無根據，業界已經非常配合政府的措施，但感覺不到政府的誠意，在無諮詢下突然收緊措施。"},{"pid":"b5a8a812b24c6edc16c3960ecffc49e9a93123d4","tid":2369624,"uid":146934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34a2beb941143a70ee782862a06dd36d223d88a7","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c775d9dccb4a9f1b662ed0e94d04650a9991651","tid":2369624,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"其實有好多酒吧偷雞開緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n灣仔果堆夜晚多人過年宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"有牌o個d 邊敢做呀<br />\n釘牌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:21:40.000Z","msg":"好多私竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a33eec43cfc6f1f888d6def6d8920226d188aa3","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804f3aa2e4b0e233b75ca67a43cfb31e5ab4c61e","tid":2369624,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"講左成年都未見大規模結業"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:22:23.000Z","msg":"冇左地方搬磚?"},{"pid":"51a797644bd7e2d34552ece11360d288b83685f6","tid":2369624,"uid":77187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae8f1b2f52df7daca9fdfa752844f95adac26d4b","tid":2369624,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a719aa6376f546fb322157cd0639417ccc4b9930","tid":2369624,"uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾成日話執<br />\n執撚三成年都仲未執得哂<br />\n真係打不死的小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2285789/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2285789/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T10:22:27.000Z","